file.name: api.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: example service
servers:
  - url: http://localhost:12000
paths:
  /item:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: item found
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Item"
components:
  schemas:
    NullableScalar:
      type: string
      nullable: true
    NullableObject:
      type: object
      nullable: true
    ItemType:
      type: string
      enum:
        - custom
        - default 
    Item:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
        - name
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
          format: name-format
          pattern: .*
        flag:
          type: boolean
        type:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/ItemType"
